SYNOPSIS (OPTIONAL)
===================
   string db_conv_string(stringÂ str)

DESCRIPTION
===========
   Convert the string <str> into a string that is correctly interpretated for 
   usage as a string in db_exec(), e.g. ' is replaced with ' and so on.

   The function is available only if the driver is compiled with mySQL 
   support. In that case, __MYSQL__ is defined.
